genresAdvancedInfo.name: indie boliviano
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Indie boliviano is a genre of music that emerged from the underground music scene in Bolivia. With influences from indie rock, folk, and traditional Bolivian music, this genre is known for its introspective lyrics and unique sound. Indie boliviano artists are gaining recognition both in Bolivia and internationally.
